data.description: Did you say master on main???  Come fall in love with this Beautiful sprawling  stepless ranch home with an upstairs bonus room in sought after Covington GA.  This single owner home  is a rare find! It was the subdivision model and has 3 bedrooms with walk in closets, an eat in kitchen, a formal dining room, a family room, and den/sunroom. Outside you will find generous parking for all your vehicles and your extra guests on the parking pad or 2 car side facing garage . Life at 15 Saddlebrook Lane provides for easy living!  Your new home has 2733 sf of living space, a NEW roof, meticulous landscaping, and home security --it is move in ready!  Take a 10 minute drive to grocery stores,  shopping, restaurants, hair and nail salons for all your errands--or take a leisurely stroll through the neighborhood on your paved sidewalks. Act now or tell a friend but don't let this one slip away!
